name: Meghan Markle
description:
Meghan Markle, widely known and beloved for her humble attitude and likeable personality, now available for Stable Diffusion. Meghan is well known for being extremely in touch with regular people, maintaining a level-headed approach to sensitive topics and exercising no entitlement whatsoever in dealing with critics and negative reactions.

The embed has been trained on SD 1.5 and works well on most 1.5 based models. It is recommended to run at a sampling rate of at least 30 to 40, otherwise the birthmarks on her forehead will do weird shit. Stable Diffusion also has a tendency to try and render Harry into pictures, add 'prince harry' to your negative prompt to prevent this.

If you enjoy my creations and want to support me or have a face you'd like to commission, consider supporting me on Buy Me A Coffee :)
